prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Track temperature, symptoms, medicine intake, and diet of registered patients.",
      "evidence_quote": "Functionalities: temperature, symptoms, medicine intake and diet of the registered patient."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "View all information of patients from screening to discharge.",
      "evidence_quote": "All the information of the patients from screening to discharge can be viewed."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Prescribe medicines to specific patients.",
      "evidence_quote": "Medicines can also be prescribed to a specific patient."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow COVID-19 patients to update data and checklist of medical shops in their locality.",
      "evidence_quote": "COVID-19 Patients: View the data shared by the doctor, home quarantined patients can update data and checklist of medical shops in their locality."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Display number of people infected (symptomatic and asymptomatic) and death in user's locality.",
      "evidence_quote": "Check the number of people infected (symptomatic and asymptomatic) and death in their locality ranging from current street, 500 m, 1 km, 5 km, 10 km"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Provide a blog where recovered persons can share their experience.",
      "evidence_quote": "view a blog where recovered persons share their experience."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow COVID-19 Essentials Seller to stock up essentials like masks and gloves according to infection in an area.",
      "evidence_quote": "COVID-19 Essentials Seller: Can stock up essentials like masks and gloves according to infection in an area."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "List medical shops nearby the area for COVID-19 Essentials Seller.",
      "evidence_quote": "Medical shops nearby the area will be listed."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Assign workers to disinfect covid affected areas regularly based on infection data for Corporation Worker Head.",
      "evidence_quote": "workers will be assigned to disinfect covid affected areas regularly based on infection data"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow Admin to update current number of infected people in a locality.",
      "evidence_quote": "Admin: updates current number of infected people in a locality."
    }
  ]
}

